name: .XMS File Extension
summary: Learn about .XMS files and view a list of programs that open them.

description: Project created and used by Music Studio, an iOS music production app; contains music project information, which includes audio tracks, song parameters, keyboard layout, effect settings, metronome settings, and interface settings.

content: While the XMS file contains many settings, it does not store preferences from the "Setup" screen. The XMS format is a proprietary format that cannot be opened by any other application.
